Caption: Dr. H. C. Heinrich Luebke, President of the Federal Republic of Germany, in conversation with people in campus
Description: Dr. h. c. Heinrich Luebke, President of the Federal Republic of Germany, Mr. R. Natarajan (first from right), Registrar, Prof. B. Sengupto (second from right), Director and Prof. D. Venkateswarlu (fifth from right), Head of Department of Chemical Engineering, are also present.
